dc_title_s: Warm Springs Hatchery, Russian River Watershed, California, 2002
dc_description_s: This point shapefile shows the location of the Warm Spirings Fish Hatchery located in the Russian River watershed region near Geyserville, California. This layer is the result of querying a larger dataset developed by the California Department of Fish and Game (CDFG). This shapefile is intended to be used for watershed planning and analysis.
